cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as vehicle detection, part localization, visibility characterization, and 3D dimension estimation. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves robotics-related tasks such as pose estimation and 3D vehicle localization, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics). The paper uses deep learning techniques, which can be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence techniques for vehicle analysis, which can be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also involves security-related tasks such as privacy and data protection, which can be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
